2001-06-14  bmh  <bmh@users.sourceforge.net>

	* /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/NEWS:
	- Updated NEWS file for 0.0.4

	* /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/configure.in, /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/ggz-gtk-client.spec, /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/Makefile.am, /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/QuickStart.GGZ, /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/README.GGZ:
	- Documentation updates
	- Bumped version to 0.0.4
	- Include docs in tarball

	* /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/src/frontend/gtk/Makefile.am, /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/man/Makefile.am, /cvsroot/ggz/gtk-client/po/Makefile.am:
	- Explicitly specify SUBDIRS = ., rather than leaving it blank.
	  Leaving it blank causes 'make dist' to choke

