	  MSGBOX_NORAML
	  MSGBOX_MODAL

	* /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/src/frontend/gtk/client.c, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/src/frontend/gtk/msgbox.c, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/src/frontend/gtk/msgbox.h:
	- changed status name to mb_status
	- changed mb_status to static
	- added a fourth varible to the function call of type MBIcon
	  MSGBOX_NONE
	  MSGBOX_STOP
	  MSGBOX_INFO

